The paper is about robotics and mapping, which falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). The paper also deals with 3D reconstruction and analysis of traversability, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper proposes an algorithm that uses machine learning techniques to modify the mesh according to 3D points updates, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
